        <svg class="tool-faq-minus hidden mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[#4f39f6]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="tool-faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-5">
        <p class="font-sans text-[14px] leading-[1.7] text-[#4b5563]">No mínimo, 2,5 cm quadrados. Para displays de mesa e cartões de balcão, entre 3,5 e 5 cm é ideal. Para cartazes de parede para escanear à distância, use entre 6 e 7,5 cm.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-b border-[#f3f4f6]">
      <button class="tool-faq-btn flex w-full cursor-pointer items-start justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-5 text-left transition-colors hover:bg-[#fafafa]" aria-expanded="false">
        <span class="font-sans text-[15px] font-semibold text-[#111827]">Os QR codes de avaliações do Google expiram?</span>
        <svg class="tool-faq-plus mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[#9ca3af]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        <svg class="tool-faq-minus hidden mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[#4f39f6]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="tool-faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-5">
        <p class="font-sans text-[14px] leading-[1.7] text-[#4b5563]">Não. O QR code codifica sua URL de avaliações do Google, que é permanente enquanto seu Perfil de Negócios no Google existir. Imprima uma vez e use por anos.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-b border-[#f3f4f6]">
      <button class="tool-faq-btn flex w-full cursor-pointer items-start justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-5 text-left transition-colors hover:bg-[#fafafa]" aria-expanded="false">
        <span class="font-sans text-[15px] font-semibold text-[#111827]">Posso personalizar a cor do meu QR code de avaliações?</span>
        <svg class="tool-faq-plus mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[#9ca3af]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
        <svg class="tool-faq-minus hidden mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[#4f39f6]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="tool-faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-5">
        <p class="font-sans text-[14px] leading-[1.7] text-[#4b5563]">Sim. Escolha entre 6 temas de cor que se aplicam tanto aos módulos do QR code quanto aos destaques do modelo de impressão. Cores escuras sobre fundos brancos oferecem a melhor confiabilidade de escaneamento.</p>
